grilo-0.1-plugins (0.1.4-1fremantle) unstable; urgency=low

  * Disabled debug
  * Disabled flickr, lastfm, metadata-store, podcasts and upnp
  * Ported code to GnomeVFS as GVFS has problems in fremantle
  * Changed youtube default mime to video/x-shockwave-flash
  * Check for NULL duration before setting it to the GrlMedia
  * Lowered version of cdbs in debian/control

 -- Xabier Rodriguez Calvar <xrcalvar@igalia.com>  Tue, 01 Jun 2010 09:41:41 +0200

